query: SELECT MIN(mc.note) AS production_note, MIN(t.title) AS movie_title, MIN(t.production_year) AS movie_year FROM company_type AS ct, info_type AS it, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, title AS t WHERE ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND it.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND mi_idx.info < '8.0' AND t.production_year > 2012 AND t.title not like '%dream%' AND t.title not like '%tree%' AND t.title not like '%diamond%' AND t.title not like '%sword%' AND t.title not like '%life%' AND ct.kind not in ('distributors','special effects companies') AND it.info in ('agent address','trade mark','LD number of chapter stops','crazy credits','LD master format','plot','LD analog right','copyright holder','LD color rendition','locations','mpaa','death notes','LD digital sound','LD picture format','filming dates','opening weekend','other works','LD laserdisc title')
left deep tree min order: ((((it join mi_idx) join ct) join mc) join t)
bushy deep tree min order: ((((it join mi_idx) join ct) join mc) join t)
